An interactive Streamlit dashboard for exploring relationships between text sentiment metrics (from company filings or financial reports) and stock return performance.

ğŸš€ Features

Visualizes correlation between sentiment and returns using Plotly scatter plots.

Interactive UI built with Streamlit.

